dct_title_s: [Topography of part of southern Santa Clara County, Calif
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and hachures.
Shows Southern Pacific Railroad tracks, proposed dam, waterways, Bay Cities Water Company, Spring Valley Water Company.
Canals with directional arrows, land divisions, roads.
Oriented with north toward upper left.
Includes inset of cross section of Coyote River "at. 'A-A.'"
"Note:- There are 16,000 Acres under this project; 62 miles of ditch; 41,500 Cu. Yds. Excavation; 18,500 Cu. Yds. of Concrete Lining. The Canals vary in size from 160 to 8 Sec. Ft. Capacity."
